{"tid":2051632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"明居正對於川普會唔會對中共趕盡殺總既睇法","createTime":"2020-06-05T02:33:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T02:42:37.000Z","uid":38962,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3546652a6755441ca05d2d3bb5e5caf4540d488e","tid":2051632,"uid":38962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T02:33:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wlaX55ipV5Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwlaX55ipV5Y&d=OUx24mKaoEPTVTG9WcU5Eqd04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=9bfdc607\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wlaX55ipV5Y</a><br />\n<br />\n重點既係<br />\n1.川普係計緊數，除左自己既總統選舉之外，仲計緊美國既利益(maga)<br />\n2.未到最後一步唔會殺中共，除非真係揾到今次暴動係中共有份大力策劃，又<br />\n或者佢再之前影片講過揾到肺炎實則証據係中共搞<br />\n3.而家佢做任何野都係覺得仲係掌握之中，包括選舉，所以無對暴動特別關注<br />\n4.盡力保住貿易協議，係咁迫中共買野<br />\n<br />\n大概係咁"},{"pid":"cdfab157fe34d93b595edbe8a4d3a1a47e5599e9","tid":2051632,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T02:34:58.000Z","msg":"好似未有有力證據係支那搞事"},{"pid":"488671ca3d5c49f856350beda8ad76f74e8260bc","tid":2051632,"uid":38962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T02:35:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=393348\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D393348&d=OUx24mKaoEPTVTG9WcU5Eqd04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=6068d873\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D393348&h=5a8cefec\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=393348</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇到呢單新聞，就知川普都係保住個貿易協議，咁佢就可以選舉用黎話點幫美國"},{"pid":"9fd69a9e7274f7cf3f2fed8a45b6119d82eba04c","tid":2051632,"uid":172627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T02:42:37.000Z","msg":"愛國主義者，點會為個人利益"}]}